businesses backed by top tier private equity and venture capital firms. His roles have included board, executive, operational, financial and business development responsibilities.<br />\n​Prior to joining FIMC as its CEO, Brian was responsible for all business affairs at an innovative healthcare company. Within two years of joining that business as its first full time employee, he raised over $60 million from three of the world’s largest pharmaceutical companies and other investors. He also helped build out the organization and oversaw the company’s P&amp;L. Earlier in his career, while serving at two other businesses, he closed 20 partnering transactions and led initiatives such as an effort to take a U.S. only business into international markets, which resulted in the company having a distribution network in 90 countries within 18 months. Brian started his career in investment banking, where he helped close $2 billion in M&amp;A transactions for clients around the world.​<br />\nBrian earned his B.S. in Finance from the University of Illinois and his M.B.A. from the Kellogg School of Management at Northwestern University, where he graduated in one year. He lives in Sarasota with his wife and three children, to whom he gladly dedicates his free time.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle --><ul class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_2 clearfix et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_right\">\n				\n				\n				<li\n            class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_2 et_pb_social_icon et_pb_social_network_link  et-social-linkedin et_pb_social_media_follow_network_2\'><a\n              href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/linkedinbrianwilliams\'\n              class=\'icon et_pb_with_border\'\n              title=\'Follow on LinkedIn\'\n               target=\"_blank\"><span\n                class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_name\'\n                aria-hidden=\'true\'\n                >Follow</span></a></li>\n			</ul> <!-- .et_pb_counters -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n				\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_8\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_15    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_9 et_always_center_on_mobile\">\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img src=\"http://mng.b0b.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Dave-Daverio-HiRes.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_9 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n					Dave Daverio\n				</div>\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_toggle et_pb_toggle_2 et_pb_toggle_item  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n				\n				\n				<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">President, USA</h5>\n				<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n					Dave Daverio serves as President at FIMC. He joined the company 19 years ago as an Account Manager. Dave brings a wide array of experience to FIMC, with his 25 years of sales expertise and focus in sales management, high-impact product presentations, new product launch and deployment strategy.<br />\nAs part of the FIMC’s Executive team, Dave is responsible for managing client relationships while being accountable for the P&amp;L of company products sold in the US and direct sales efforts for the company with his team through financial institutions and other business channels. He achieved record growth in multiple areas of the country and was presented with numerous awards for achieving goals at FIMC. Dave attended the University of Akron before relocating to Sarasota, FL. Dave and his wife, Valerie, have one Daughter, named Alexa.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle --><ul class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_3 clearfix et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_right\">\n				\n				\n				<li\n            class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_3 et_pb_social_icon et_pb_social_network_link  et-social-linkedin et_pb_social_media_follow_network_3\'><a\n              href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave-daverio-74846a31\'\n              class=\'icon et_pb_with_border\'\n              title=\'Follow on LinkedIn\'\n               target=\"_blank\"><span\n                class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_name\'\n                aria-hidden=\'true\'\n                >Follow</span></a></li>\n			</ul> <!-- .et_pb_counters -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n				\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_9\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_16    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_10 et_always_center_on_mobile\">\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img src=\"http://mng.b0b.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Rob-Raymond-HiRes.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_10 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n					Robert Raymond\n				</div>\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_toggle et_pb_toggle_3 et_pb_toggle_item  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n				\n				\n				<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">President, Canada</h5>\n				<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n					Rob Raymond joined FIMC in 2001 to launch and build the Canadian arm of FIMC. With twenty years of experience in the roadside assistance and ancillary product market, Robert understands that all decisions must ultimately be made to best serve the end user.<br />\nRob earned both his Bachelor&#8217;s and Master&#8217;s degree from The University of Western Ontario and has since worked in many distribution channels, ranging from direct sales to automotive-aftermarket and consumer finance. He is passionate and enthusiastic about the sale and promotion of useful, valuable benefits that suit different needs.<br />\nRobert currently lives in Ontario, Canada with his wife and family, they make sure to visit Sarasota frequently.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle --><ul class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_4 clearfix et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_right\">\n				\n				\n				<li\n            class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_4 et_pb_social_icon et_pb_social_network_link  et-social-linkedin et_pb_social_media_follow_network_4\'><a\n              href=\'https://ca.linkedin.com/in/robertraymonduwo\'\n              class=\'icon et_pb_with_border\'\n              title=\'Follow on LinkedIn\'\n               target=\"_blank\"><span\n                class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_name\'\n                aria-hidden=\'true\'\n                >Follow</span></a></li>\n			</ul> <!-- .et_pb_counters -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n				\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_10\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_17    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_11 et_always_center_on_mobile\">\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img src=\"http://mng.b0b.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Murat-Camoglu-HiRes.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_11 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n					Murat Camoglu\n				</div>\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_toggle et_pb_toggle_4 et_pb_toggle_item  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n				\n				\n				<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Chief Financial Officer</h5>\n				<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n					Murat has twenty years of experience at both publicly traded &amp; sponsor backed global organizations in branded consumer goods and technology products.<br />\nPrior to joining FIMC, Murat served as Chief Financial Officer of SteelSeries, a sponsor-backed global consumer technology business. Earlier, he served as the CFO of Grohe Americas, a leading premium sanitary fittings provider, where he successfully increased profitability; drove operational improvements and helped build out the organization. He also worked as divisional CFO of Grohe AG based in Germany.<br />\nPrior to Grohe, Murat held various financial and strategic positions at Diageo, a leading premium beverage business. He served as Global Director of White Spirits Category with over $1 billion in sales and as Finance Director of major markets in USA and Europe, with over $200 million in sales. He started his career in banking where he helped execute $10 billion in M&amp;A transactions for clients globally.​<br />\nMurat holds an MBA in Private Equity &amp; Entrepreneurial Management from The Wharton School, University of Pennsylvania; and BSBA, cum laude, in Finance &amp; International Business from Georgetown University.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n				\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_11\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_18    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_12 et_always_center_on_mobile\">\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img src=\"http://mng.b0b.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Sean-OReilly-HiRes.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_12 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n					Sean O&#8217;Reilly\n				</div>\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_toggle et_pb_toggle_5 et_pb_toggle_item  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n				\n				\n				<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Chief Growth Officer</h5>\n				<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n					Sean is the Chief Growth officer for FIMC, responsible for Product Development, Marketing, Marketing Analytics and New Channel Growth.<br />\nFor the past twenty years, Sean has held a variety of executive roles in marketing and operations for Leo Burnett, USAA, J.P. Morgan Chase and J.G Wentworth after beginning his career as a U.S. Army officer. Sean launched the highly successful Chase Sapphire card and grew the business through online, branch, and direct marketing efforts while at J.P. Morgan Chase. Prior to joining FIMC, Sean consulted with startup and mid-market financial services and life sciences companies on a variety of strategic initiatives.<br />\nSean earned his B.B.A. in Finance and Business Economics from The University of Notre Dame, and he currently serves on the Board of Directors for the Notre Dame Alumni Association. He received his MBA from The Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania.<br />\n​Sean and his wife Sara and their four children, Maureen, Bridget, Delaney and Patrick live in the Philadelphia area.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle --><ul class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_5 clearfix et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_right\">\n				\n				\n				<li\n            class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_5 et_pb_social_icon et_pb_social_network_link  et-social-linkedin et_pb_social_media_follow_network_5\'><a\n              href=\'https://www.linkedin.com/in/seanporeilly\'\n              class=\'icon et_pb_with_border\'\n              title=\'Follow on LinkedIn\'\n               target=\"_blank\"><span\n                class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_name\'\n                aria-hidden=\'true\'\n                >Follow</span></a></li>\n			</ul> <!-- .et_pb_counters -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n				\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_12\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_19    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_13 et_always_center_on_mobile\">\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img src=\"http://mng.b0b.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Bill-Costa-HiRes-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_13 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\">\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n					Bill Costa\n				</div>\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_toggle et_pb_toggle_6 et_pb_toggle_item  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n				\n				\n				<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Chief Information Officer</h5>\n				<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n					Bill Costa re-joined FIMC in March of 2014 as Chief Information Officer. Prior to FIMC, Mr. Costa served in executive management in various industries including Health Care, Environmental Sciences, Management Consulting, Financial Services, Local Government Services, and Mortgage Services.<br />\nMr. Costa has a Bachelor&#8217;s of Science degree in Information Technology from Rutgers University, and brings more than 32 years of experience in Information Technology. His progressive experience spans most IT disciplines, methodologies, and best practices for strategic delivery of Information Technology solutions.\n				</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle_content -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_toggle --><ul class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_6 clearfix et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_right\">\n				\n				\n				<li\n            class=\'et_pb_social_media_follow_network_6 et_pb_social_icon et_pb_social_network_link  e